reen pendant lighting.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-15-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-15-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-15-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561071\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561071\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-16-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy kitchen with yellow walls, a white countertop, and warm lighting. A wooden floor leads to an archway revealing light blue cabinetry and a brick accent wall. A small plant is on a shelf.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-16-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-16-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-16-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-16-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561072\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561072\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/La-Maison-Perron-Quebec-Perron-17-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy living room with a brown sofa, yellow ottoman, and a TV. A person sits at a pink table, and colorful decor, including wall art and plants, adds vibrancy